===== Troubleshooting =====


========
CONTENTS
========
	01 - Info
	02 - Main Source of Issues
	03 - Basic MHM Install
	04 - Extended MHM Install


=========
01 - Info
=========
	* The following sections will cover what should be, and what may be, in your "~mods" folder.
	* Things that are not listed are likely to be the culprit for your issues.
	* At this stage, this is based on the AIO version of MHM (not individual modules version), but is still largely applicable (TODO)
	* This only covers MHM, its addons, and its officially recommended mods


==========================
02 - Main Source of Issues
==========================
	* Make double sure that you have ~NOT~ installed any of LNA file other than "LNA01_99_P.pak"
	* Make double sure that you have ~NOT~ installed "OXA03_P.pak" from OXA
	* Make sure that you are using the "LocalizationDB_P.*" files from MHM and not some other mod
	* Make sure to get rid of obsolete texture files from older versions of MHM and previsously required mods:
	    - xxxPillhead_Textures.(pak,ucas,utoc)
	    - Ziv_RepairKitBundle_Textures.(pak,ucas,utoc)
	    - MHMTextures.(pak,ucas,utoc)                    <-- New versions are called "zzzzzzz_MHMTextures0z_P.*"
	* Make sure to not use "Vanilla_AIGlobals_XRay_Fix_P.pak" if using Core Module, AIO, or A-Life Found a Way.
	* Mods that are not recommended by the author of MHM


======================
03 - Basic MHM Install
======================
	For a standard MHM AIO setup, without any of the official addons, or recommended mods, your "~mods" folder should contain --ONLY-- the following:

		LNA01_99_P				(pak)
		LocalizationDB_P			(pak,ucas,utoc)		    (from MHM_AIO, not from any other mod)
		OXA0X					(pak,ucas,utoc)
		OXA01_P					(pak,ucas,utoc)
		OXA02_P					(pak,ucas,utoc)
		Simple_ModLoader			(pak,ucas,utoc)
		Simple_ModLoader_0_P			(pak)
		zz_FactionsPatch_Textures_P		(pak,ucas,utoc)
		ZZ_Mutant_Loot_Textures_P		(pak,ucas,utoc)
		ZZZ_ProjectItemization-Textures_P	(pak,ucas,utoc)
		zzzzzzz_MHMTextures0z_P			(pak,ucas,utoc)
		zzzzzzz_MHM_Interface0z_P		(pak,ucas,utoc)
		
		zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Standard	(pak)
			--OR--
		zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Hardcore	(pak)


=========================
